QME, one of the leading global mining and tunnelling contractors, is pleased to announce their participation at PDAC 2018. At the renowned event, QME will be showcasing their latest equipment and solutions for contract mining and tunnelling projects. The PDAC International Convention, Trade Show & Investors Exchange will be held between the 4th and 7th March at the Metro Toronto Convention Centre, Toronto, Canada. The event attracts more than 24,000 attendees from more than 130 countries around the globe. QME invite you to join them at the exhibition at Booth TS 0938, located in the Main Trade Show Hall of the Metro Toronto Convention Centre.